🎯 KEY RSB PATTERN ADOPTIONS
----------------------------
1. Composition over Inheritance
   - Use traits for width calculation
   - Pluggable theme and layout strategies

2. Functional Core, Imperative Shell
   - Pure width/layout functions
   - Impure CLI and I/O at edges

3. Performance Considerations
   - Zero-copy stream processing
   - Lazy evaluation of layouts
   - Minimal allocations

